                <h1>Caution Sign Meanings Explained</h1>
                <p>Caution signs are crucial safety indicators, warning of potential hazards like wet floors, construction areas, or electrical dangers. They feature bold colors, typically yellow, to catch attention. Understanding these signs helps individuals stay alert and avoid accidents, making environments safer for everyone.</p>
